sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Validating Webhook<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Operator as OGX Operator<br/>(OGXServerReconciler)
    participant Kustomize as Manifest Pipeline<br/>(kustomize + plugins)
    participant OGXServer as OGX Server Pod<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over User, OCI: Flow 1: OGXServer Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply OGXServer CR
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-ogx-io-v1beta1-ogxserver<br/>mTLS (API server cert)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: CR created/rejected

    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (OGXServer created/updated)<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token

    Operator->>OCI: GET image labels (distribution config)<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+, registry credentials
    OCI-->>Operator: Base config.yaml from OCI labels

    Operator->>Kustomize: Render manifests (base YAML + plugins)
    Kustomize-->>Operator: Rendered resources (Deployment, Service, PVC, etc.)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-Side Apply (SSA) managed resources<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Applied resources

    Operator->>OGXServer: GET /v1/health (health check)<br/>HTTP/8321, no auth
    OGXServer-->>Operator: Health status
    Operator->>OGXServer: GET /v1/providers<br/>HTTP/8321, no auth
    OGXServer-->>Operator: Provider info
    Operator->>OGXServer: GET /v1/version<br/>HTTP/8321, no auth
    OGXServer-->>Operator: Version info

    Operator->>K8sAPI: PATCH OGXServer/status<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Status updated

    Note over User, OCI: Flow 2: Legacy Resource Adoption (LlamaStack → OGX)

    User->>K8sAPI: Annotate OGXServer with adoption annotation
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event (annotation detected)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Scale down legacy LlamaStackDistribution Deployment to 0<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Deployment scaled

    Operator->>K8sAPI: List pods, wait for termination<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Pods terminated (RWO PVC released)

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Detach PVC ownerRef from legacy CR<br/>Label PVC for discovery<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: PVC updated

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Transfer Service/Ingress ownership<br/>Replace controller ownerRef<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Ownership transferred

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update OGXServer status (adoption complete)<br/>HTTPS/443
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Status updated
